    <title lang="en-gb">board3 Portal Add-On - Gallery Block</title>
	<title lang="de">board3 Portal Erweiterung - Galerie-Block</title>
    <description lang="en-gb"><![CDATA[Gallery Block for your board3 Portal.]]></description>
	<description lang="de"><![CDATA[Fügt ein Galerie-Block deinem board3 Portal hinzu.]]></description>
    <author-notes lang="en-gb"><![CDATA[Support for this extension can be found on phpbb-projekt.de]]></author-notes>
	<author-notes lang="de"><![CDATA[Support für diese Erweiterung findest du auf phpbb-projekt.de]]></author-notes>
    <author-group>
      <author>
        <realname>Christian</realname>
        <username>Christian_N</username>
        <homepage>http://www.phpbb-projekt.de</homepage>
        <contributions />
      </author>
     </author-group>
    <mod-version>1.2.3</mod-version>
	<link-group>
		<link type="template" lang="de" href="contrib/subsilver2.xml">Anleitung für das Style subsilver2</link>
		<link type="template" lang="en-gb" href="contrib/subsilver2.xml">Manual for subsilver2 Style</link>
		<link type="language" lang="de" href="contrib/de.xml">Anleitung für das deutsche Sprachpaket</link>
		<link type="language" lang="en-gb" href="contrib/de.xml">Manual for German Language-set</link>
	</link-group>
    <installation>
      <level>easy</level>
      <time>300</time>
      <target-version>3.0.4</target-version>
    </installation>
  </header>
  <action-group>
    <copy>
		<file from="root/styles/prosilver/template/portal/block/*.*" to="styles/prosilver/template/portal/block/*.*" />
		<file from="root/portal/language/en/mods/gallery_block.php" to="portal/language/en/mods/gallery_block.php" />
		<file from="root/install/*.*" to="install/*.*" />
    </copy>
    <open src="adm/index.php">
      <edit>
		<comment lang="en-gb">Remove this Code...</comment>
		<comment lang="de">Entfernen diese Code...</comment>
        <find><![CDATA[$user->add_lang('mods/gallery_block');]]></find>
        <action type="replace-with"><![CDATA[]]></action>
      </edit>
    </open>
    <open src="portal/block/additional_blocks.php">
      <edit>
        <find><![CDATA[if (!defined('IN_PORTAL'))
{
	exit;
}]]></find>
        <action type="after-add"><![CDATA[if ($portal_config['portal_gallery'] or ( $portal_config['portal_gallery_center'] && $load_center === TRUE ) )
{
	include($phpbb_root_path . 'portal/block/album.'.$phpEx);
}]]></action>
      </edit>
    </open>
    <open src="portal/includes/lang_adm_additional_blocks.php">
      <edit>
        <find><![CDATA[$user->add_lang('mods/info_acp_portal');]]></find>
        <action type="after-add"><![CDATA[$user->add_lang('mods/gallery_block');]]></action>
      </edit>
    </open>
    <open src="styles/prosilver/template/portal/block/additional_blocks_center.html">
      <edit>
        <find><![CDATA[<!-- additional_blocks //-->]]></find>
        <action type="after-add"><![CDATA[<!-- IF S_DISPLAY_GALLERY_CENTER -->
	<!-- INCLUDE portal/block/album_center.html -->
<!-- ENDIF -->]]></action>
      </edit>
    </open>
    <open src="styles/prosilver/template/portal/block/additional_blocks_right.html">
	  <edit>
        <find><![CDATA[<!-- additional_blocks //-->]]></find>
        <action type="after-add"><![CDATA[<!-- IF S_DISPLAY_GALLERY -->
	<!-- INCLUDE portal/block/album_small.html -->
<!-- ENDIF -->]]></action>
      </edit>
    </open>
	<diy-instructions lang="de"><![CDATA[Rufe install/ auf und führe den Installer aus

Leere den Cache im "Administrations-Bereich" (ACP) > "Allgemein" > "Den Cache leeren"

Aktualisiere deine Styles:
    "Administrations-Bereich" (ACP) > "Styles" > "Templates" > jedes > "Aktualisieren"
    "Administrations-Bereich" (ACP) > "Styles" > "Themes" > jedes > "Aktualisieren"
    "Administrations-Bereich" (ACP) > "Styles" > "Grafiksammlungen" > jedes > "Aktualisieren"
]]></diy-instructions>
	<diy-instructions lang="en-gb"><![CDATA[Browse to install/ and run the installer

Clear your cache in the "Administration Control Panel" (ACP) > "General" > "Purge the cache"

Refresh your Styles:
    "Administration Control Panel" (ACP) > "Styles" > "Templates" > each > "refresh"
    "Administration Control Panel" (ACP) > "Styles" > "Themes" > each > "refresh"
    "Administration Control Panel" (ACP) > "Styles" > "Imagesets" > each > "refresh"
]]></diy-instructions>
</action-group>
</mod>